\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 What I study in this project\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 \strokec2 Forecast development and evaluation
\f1\b0 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 I develop near-term ecological forecasts and evaluate them against new observations, quantifying forecast accuracy, uncertainty, and sources of error.\

\f0\b \strokec2 Predictability and temporal dynamics
\f1\b0 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 I examine how response lags and transient dynamics influence the ability to anticipate ecological change, and how predictability varies across systems and timescales.\

\f0\b \strokec2 Data integration and synthesis
\f1\b0 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 I work on integrating heterogeneous ecological data into forecasting workflows and on synthesizing forecasts across models and datasets.\

\f0\b \strokec2 Capacity building and coordination
\f1\b0 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 A key component of this project is supporting training and coordination in ecological forecasting, including shared databases, standards, and educational resources.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
